OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly dry
OL,6,Fevening and night with plenty of clear
OL,7,Fspells. Some low cloud developing over
OL,8,Fthe hills during the early hours,
OL,9,Fthick enough for the odd shower over
OL,10,Fthe mountains. Staying mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FSome low cloud first thing,
OL,13,Fwith perhaps an isolated light shower.
OL,14,FSkies brightening by lunchtime, with
OL,15,Fplenty of sunshine developing.
OL,16,FGenerally feeling fresher than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
